abid.title: There should be a workflow to change the AbID prefix for an existing AbID when it changes size

comments.body: The old system had a pop-up that asked if you "do want to replace the AbID"

I've deleted that AbID from the system like this, to unblock Michael:

```ruby
item = Alma::BibItem.find_by_barcode("32101113873150")
holding_id = item["holding_data"]["holding_id"]
abid = AbsoluteIdentifier.where(holding_id: holding_id)
abid.last.destroy
```
